name: Dataviz
tagline: This is a repository to share ongoing work building animated HIV cohort data visualizations.
body:
# dAtaViz
This is the temporary location of the data visualization scripts. These scripts take as input data that is formatted using a known convention in HIV research - the `CCASAnet DTP` which is based on [HICDEP](http://hicdep.org).
